Willie Tyrone TROTTIE, petitioner,
v.
William STEPHENS, Director, Texas Department of Criminal Justice, Correctional Institutions Division. No. 13-7367. Supreme Court of the United States March 24, 2014. Case below, 720 F.3d 231 .
